summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning, amending Plat 232W, page 26 of the Official Land Use Map, to rezone approximately 3,378 square feet of property located at 934 North 98th Street from Single Family 5000 (SF5000) to Lowrise 3 (L3). (Petition of Mary Kesinger, C.F. 300205)
committee: Housing, Community Development and Urban Environment
